{"tid":1767121,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想報仇","createTime":"2019-12-03T05:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T12:51:54.000Z","uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"84e27db915bedd423a8b11dd46c1eb434ca57639","tid":1767121,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"發現女朋友個WhatsApp 有同第二個男仔有纏綿對話<br />\n我知道個男仔有參加社會又搞衝擊<br />\n宜家想搞佢罪証再報警篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c139948bd9899e7d68f5d5700bf45f2d6fde48c","tid":1767121,"uid":198590,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#165028 - 天安門旅遊</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>誠哥真係好醒目 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsosad.gif&h=5e5c7195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fclown.gif&h=b82ebc3d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Ffrown.gif&h=dc0d24e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>好怕d勇武派 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>（求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsosad.gif&h=5e5c7195&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"90c4b063afe8baa43a3dd9dc82cb33ea62f77c6d","tid":1767121,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"殺狗"},{"pid":"fb634a5bd5878337df94554679543fe32914342e","tid":1767121,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"係你嘅就係你既 唔係你